The front is 100% cotton polka dot print in aqua
On the back is teal colored minky dot.

On the front, a fun cotton print in pink, fuchsia, kelly green and light blue.
Super soft hot pink colored minky dot (polyester) on the back.
Un-looped ribbons are sewn securely into the seams and the edges are heat sealed to prevent fraying.
A ribbon loop at the top allows you to use a plastic toy ring (not included) to attach the toy to a stroller, car seat or activity mat.
Appliqu√©d eyes and beak made from wool blend felt
Filled with polyester fiber made from recycled plastic bottles.

Machine washable in cool water on gentle cycle. Tumble dry low or air dry.
Measures approximately 10cm tall by 10cm wide at the bottom.
